{"tid":1842533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣] 我知大家好驚 但係今次機會過咗就冇","createTime":"2020-01-25T17:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T01:04:21.000Z","uid":258808,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6ca28650df64d3e7e40cc6b833348d4883551421","tid":1842533,"uid":258808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T17:51:40.000Z","msg":"熱門好多po都係講緊肺炎，冇乜人討論下呢幾日到底有咩行動，睇到亂晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知呢排新年，大家又好驚自己會中招，但係今次企喺最前線嘅醫護更加需要各位嘅支持<br />\n<br />\n好似隔離po咁講，唔係一句支持佢哋罷工就夠，最起碼都可以幫手宣傳，話俾醫護手足知佢哋應該點做，仲有好多野我地可以幫<br />\n<br />\n而家要做嘅就係好好利用肺炎向政府施壓，話俾林奠條臭閪知一日唔封關我地都會繼續癱瘓醫療，更重要嘅就係用呢個機會connect更多人反鳩政府，爭取五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0FKebgf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0FKebgf.jpg&h=78e60682&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KBKJO2W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKBKJO2W.jpg&h=c36d4017&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ywCjnnX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FywCjnnX.jpg&h=fecaaf3b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zFOyrPC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzFOyrPC.jpg&h=90ea065a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLUbgi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLUbgi.jpg&h=26b5b89a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VRMgpBj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVRMgpBj.jpg&h=73849106&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vnXSHpp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvnXSHpp.jpg&h=b9b31803&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TPtiCXL.jpg